## 🎨 Theme Customization

Change your theme by updating the ThemeProvider in `src/web/main.tsx`:

```jsx
<ThemeProvider theme="elegant" mode="light">
  <App />
</ThemeProvider>
```

Available themes: `base` | `elegant` | `metro` | `studio` | `vivid`
Available modes: `light` | `dark`

